text:
Fue... "The VR Experience of Crossing
a Plank Spanning Between Buildings"...

O-Oh, it done got me all shook up~! The wind's a-howlin',
and this here plank under my feet is a-shakin'!!

There's only so much I can take! Lookin' down
makes me go 'Whoa~~!', so I can't even sneak a peek!!

Ah... Kogane-chan...
Looks like you can try again...
Shall we... give it another try...?

I reckon I'll just tumble right down again~!
Mamimi, Kiriko~! Y'all take over~~~!!
